      "content": "thanks. i'll try the water and maybe some ibuprofen. do you think i should take more if it comes back? like, i've heard some people say taking a higher dose of ibuprofen helps with those really sharp \"nerve\" pains. i just don't want it to hit me that hard again while i'm trying to study.",
